{"tid":629993,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想知長沙灣點解唔係讀長沙「灣」","createTime":"2018-04-15T07:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T08:41:17.000Z","uid":136485,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"06978d3d168353499c71715d3bea62f8ce457b3e","tid":629993,"uid":136485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"好多人都係讀長沙「環」，究竟點解唔係讀做長沙「灣」呢"},{"pid":"1901484fd3404b91138b7256e9b06a3d8c114b6a","tid":629993,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"好聽啲"},{"pid":"c71ba876370d34b16e473c1f00a8d80ff14ce679","tid":629993,"uid":135767,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:48:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b77bbf7c444a745484fef06381bab6ec77720559","tid":629993,"uid":29405,"like":10,"dislike":54,"score":-44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"有人讀灣，有人鍾意讀灣<br />\n我就讀灣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfbf31a53756723a99de64c7d3b96a59c614aba","tid":629993,"uid":16666,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"quote":{"pid":"b77bbf7c444a745484fef06381bab6ec77720559","tid":629993,"uid":29405,"like":10,"dislike":54,"score":-44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"有人讀灣，有人鍾意讀灣<br />\n我就讀灣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/155343_74c5b25f02269799d125a3505cd11c6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F155343_74c5b25f02269799d125a3505cd11c6f.png&h=9497cd48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b915ecdfcbdfa1d8ed5a7d6f5073b0ba2ec74337","tid":629993,"uid":172464,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"灣轉讀環<br />\n<br />\n作者：　潘國森<br />\n<br />\n原載：　《都市日報》〈中國名堂〉　2007年1月16日<br />\n<br />\n香港海岸線多曲折，便常以灣為地名。讀者問灣字在廣府話中轉讀為「環」的原則。<br />\n<br />\n「長沙灣」和「土瓜灣」的「灣」字，香港人口語都讀作「長沙(環)」和「土瓜(環)」，而不讀「長沙(彎)」和「土瓜(彎)」；但「筲箕灣」和「淺水灣」又不一樣。此外，「銅鑼灣」應該讀作「銅鑼(彎)」還是「銅鑼(環)」呢?<br />\n<br />\n我們可以用聲調來分析一下。灣是陰平聲，環是陽平聲，三字詞的音樂感與兩字詞不同，兩字的如馬（陽上）灣、柴（陽平）灣、深（陰平）灣都沒有變讀。長沙「環」（陽平、陰平、陽平）土瓜「環」（陰上、陰平、陽平），變讀後更順口，按原來的聲調聽起來是怪怪的。筲箕灣（陰平、陰平、陰平）和淺水灣（陰上、陰上、陰平）不用變。銅鑼「彎」（陽平、陽平、陰平）也有人讀，比長沙「彎」更可接受，不過遠不及銅鑼「環」（陽平、陽平、陽平）多。所以該從眾讀「銅鑼環」。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://www.cantoneseculture.com/page_Poon01/poonMetroHK20070116.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cantoneseculture.com%2Fpage_Poon01%2FpoonMetroHK20070116.aspx&d=f8iRq13rN6MEZzm0wnae02i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ddd7b427\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cantoneseculture.com/page_Poon01/poonMetroHK20070116.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"5cc8c0766fc2b787f958b5cefd95bf4806e9ea66","tid":629993,"uid":29405,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7dfbf31a53756723a99de64c7d3b96a59c614aba","tid":629993,"uid":16666,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"quote":{"pid":"b77bbf7c444a745484fef06381bab6ec77720559","tid":629993,"uid":29405,"like":10,"dislike":54,"score":-44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"有人讀灣，有人鍾意讀灣<br />\n我就讀灣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/155343_74c5b25f02269799d125a3505cd11c6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F155343_74c5b25f02269799d125a3505cd11c6f.png&h=9497cd48&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"唔信問下南極菇熊"},{"pid":"06bb185f3370f42aadf1a1152bbcc3c6bf3535a9","tid":629993,"uid":45749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"因為銅鑼環讀鑼環灣"},{"pid":"a8006950657902fd101a5d1c89702fdad8a41eaa","tid":629993,"uid":164771,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"西灣河